// Developer Guide: ReactorCLI1. Building the CrateReactorCLI is a standard Rust crate.cargo build
// 2. Extending SourcesTo add a new configuration source (e.g., AWS Parameter Store), implement the ConfigSource trait:impl ConfigSource for AwsParamStore {
//     fn get(&self, key: &str) -> Option<String> {
//         // ... fetch from AWS ...
//     }
// }
// 3. Polyglot SchemaThe schema definition is stored in src/schema.rs. It maps Rust types to a language-agnostic JSON format used by Fusion Forge to build bindings.
